---
title: Scenario 1 — Normal Transfer (Happy Path)
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Button as Transfer Button
    participant ParentVM as ParentViewModel
    participant Coord as TransferCoordinator
    participant Cache as SourceCache
    participant LeftBox as Left AnimatedListBox
    participant RightBox as Right AnimatedListBox

    User->>Button: Click →

    Note over ParentVM: StampTransfer BEFORE cache.Edit
    Button->>ParentVM: TransferLeftToRightCommand.Execute(itemVm)
    ParentVM->>Coord: StampTransfer(id, ToSibling, FromSibling)
    Note over Coord: _exits[id] = ToSibling\n_entries[id] = FromSibling

    ParentVM->>Cache: cache.Edit(IsOnRight = true)

    par DynamicData propagates synchronously
        Cache-->>LeftBox: CollectionChanged (Remove)
        Cache-->>RightBox: CollectionChanged (Add)
    end

    Note over LeftBox: ClassifyChange\nHasAnyPendingReason() = true\n→ ChangeType.Transfer
    Note over RightBox: ClassifyChange\nHasAnyPendingReason() = true\n→ ChangeType.Transfer

    LeftBox->>LeftBox: Transfer jumps queue\n_pipelineBusy = false\nno snap needed (idle)
    RightBox->>RightBox: Transfer jumps queue\n_pipelineBusy = false\nno snap needed (idle)

    par Both process on same dispatcher tick
        LeftBox->>LeftBox: DiffVisible → BeginExit(item)
        LeftBox->>Coord: ConsumeExitReason(id) → ToSibling
        LeftBox->>LeftBox: RunSlide(container, Right, out)\nTranslate: 0 → +width

        RightBox->>RightBox: DiffVisible → insert item
        RightBox->>RightBox: PrepareContainerForItemOverride
        RightBox->>Coord: ConsumeEntryReason(id) → FromSibling
        RightBox->>RightBox: RunSlide(container, Right, in)\nTranslate: -width → 0
    end

    Note over LeftBox,RightBox: Both animations run simultaneously (200ms)\nItem appears to fly from left list into right list

    LeftBox->>LeftBox: Animation complete\nVisibleItems.Remove(item)\n_inflightCount → 0
    RightBox->>RightBox: Animation complete\nTranslate snapped to 0\n_inflightCount → 0

    par Both gates release
        LeftBox->>LeftBox: OnAllAnimationsComplete\n_pipelineBusy = false
        RightBox->>RightBox: OnAllAnimationsComplete\n_pipelineBusy = false
    end
